Here's the PlantUML sequence diagram for the `s-sokolko_smev3_adapter_service` focusing on data flow:

```plantuml
@startuml s-sokolko_smev3_adapter_service
participant Client
participant "API Layer\n(views.py)" as API
participant "Query Processor\n(query.py)" as Processor
participant "SMEV3 Adapter\n(adapter.py)" as Adapter
participant "Schema Loader\n(loader.py)" as Schema
participant "MongoDB" as DB

Client -> API: HTTP Request (POST /schedule_query)
API -> Processor: Process request
Processor -> Schema: Validate request schema
Schema --> Processor: Validation result
Processor -> Adapter: Send SOAP request
Adapter -> SMEV3_System: SOAP call
SMEV3_System --> Adapter: SOAP response
Adapter --> Processor: Processed response
Processor -> DB: Store request data
DB --> Processor: Storage confirmation
Processor --> API: Response data
API -> Client: HTTP Response

... Polling loop ...

Processor -> Adapter: Check for responses
Adapter -> SMEV3_System: Poll SOAP request
SMEV3_System --> Adapter: SOAP response (if available)
Adapter --> Processor: Processed response
Processor -> DB: Update request status/data
DB --> Processor: Storage confirmation
@enduml
```